import { Button, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'
import { Container, ImgContainer, InfoContainer, Image } from './style'
function Slider() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <ImgContainer>
                <Image src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483985988355-763728e1935b?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=870&q=80" />
            </ImgContainer>
            <InfoContainer>
                <Typography variant="h2">Summer Sale</Typography>
                <Typography variant="h6">
                    Don't compormise on style! get flat 30% off for new arrivals
                </Typography>
                <Button style={{ backgroundColor: 'black' }}>Shop Now</Button>
            </InfoContainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Slider
